@Node Future "What can you expect."

I would like to add a rename function to the "Perform action", but since LhA doesn't support that, I'll have to extract, delete and then add under a new name - very complex and risky - I could also make a little utility to do that, but that'll mean that it's no longer one script (but who cares?).

Make some kind of config part, so you don't need to change output window size etc. in the script.
 This will also give you some filerequesters in the start, if it couldn't find MultiView, LhA etc. and then store it to EnvArc: for next use.

